---
title: Beef Chilli Burrito Bowl with Tomato Salsa, Greek Style Natural Yoghurt and Cheese
description: This Beef Chilli Burrito Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF-Y23-R03-W50-UK-QF11128-24-Main-low-8291f610.jpg
